      <title>肯尼亚立法者同意恢复引发抗议的税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/kenyan-lawmakers-agree-to-reinstate-taxes-that-ignited-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚立法者批准恢复政府在今年早些时候在数千人走上街头抗议后同意放弃的一些税收措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/kenyan-lawmakers-agree-to-reinstate-taxes-that-ignited-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 17:10:35 GMT</pubDate>
