    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择福尔肯德担任贝森特的财政部副部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-poised-to-pick-faulkender-as-deputy-treasury-secretary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普选择了金融学教授迈克尔·福尔肯德 (Michael Faulkender) 担任财政部副部长，福尔肯德在其第一任总统任期内实施了一项关键的疫情时期救助计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-poised-to-pick-faulkender-as-deputy-treasury-secretary</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 17:01:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普财政部长将与共和党参议员会面，讨论美联储和关税问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bessent-to-meet-with-gop-s-thune-with-fed-and-tariffs-on-agenda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将上任的参议院共和党领袖约翰·图恩表示，他预计将在提名听证会前讨论财政部长提名人斯科特·贝森特对关税和美联储的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bessent-to-meet-with-gop-s-thune-with-fed-and-tariffs-on-agenda</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利国会为博里奇赢得胜利，成立公共安全部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/chile-congress-creates-public-security-ministry-in-win-for-boric</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利国会最终批准了成立公共安全部的法案，这对总统加布里埃尔·博里奇来说是一项胜利，他的政府将加大打击犯罪的力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/chile-congress-creates-public-security-ministry-in-win-for-boric</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏格兰取消儿童福利上限 挑战工党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/scotland-to-remove-child-benefit-cap-in-challenge-to-labour-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏格兰政府计划取消对儿童福利的限制，这是执政的苏格兰民族党高调采取的举措，旨在挑战工党在今年英国大选中取得巨大胜利后保留的一项有争议的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/scotland-to-remove-child-benefit-cap-in-challenge-to-labour-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:23:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命彼得·纳瓦罗为贸易和制造业顾问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-taps-peter-navarro-as-trade-and-manufacturing-counselor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普任命彼得·纳瓦罗为其贸易和制造业高级顾问，将这位曾被监禁的顾问提升回与上一届特朗普政府中类似的职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-taps-peter-navarro-as-trade-and-manufacturing-counselor</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:12:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择曾进行过私人太空行走的亿万富翁来领导 NASA</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-picks-jared-isaacman-as-nasa-administrator</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将提名金融科技亿万富翁、资深 SpaceX 宇航员贾里德·艾萨克曼担任下一任 NASA 局长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-picks-jared-isaacman-as-nasa-administrator</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长拉加德称欧盟共同融资是“可取的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-s-lagarde-says-common-eu-financing-is-desirable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，她赞成欧盟为安全、气候转型等共同利益进行联合融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-s-lagarde-says-common-eu-financing-is-desirable</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普考虑用德桑蒂斯取代赫格塞斯出任五角大楼国防部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-considers-replacing-hegseth-with-desantis-as-pentagon-head</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的团队正在考虑用佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯取代陷入困境的国防部长提名人皮特·赫格塞斯，这一交换将使这位曾经的竞争对手晋升到内阁主要职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-considers-replacing-hegseth-with-desantis-as-pentagon-head</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:13:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国反对派试图弹劾尹永哲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korea-opposition-party-seeks-to-impeach-yoon-for-treason-m49amyj3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈短暂实施戒严令，导致国家陷入政治危机。此后，韩国反对派提出弹劾动议，加大了对他的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korea-opposition-party-seeks-to-impeach-yoon-for-treason-m49amyj3</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 02:53:21 GMT</pubDate>
